# Claude Code workspace — default-deny, explicit-allow.
# Ignore everything dropped under .claude/ so future PRDs, wireframes,
# scratch notes, prompts, per-user state, etc. don't accidentally land
# in the public repo. Add a `!` exception below for anything the team
# genuinely wants tracked.
.claude/*
!.claude/audits/
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/settings.json
# PRDs are forward-looking roadmap docs — tracked so they survive
# across machines and are visible to teammates. Other subdirs under
# .claude/context/ (wireframes, scratch) stay ignored by default;
# add further `!.claude/context/<subdir>/` exceptions when needed.
!.claude/context/
.claude/context/*
!.claude/context/prd/
!.claude/context/prd/**

# Local mockups / audit artifacts (kept untracked per user preference)
audit-final/
mockups/
.pentest-*/
